Static methods only have access to static objects/variables directly. In order to use any instance you will need to supply it as a parameter. 

Because you&#39;re accessing an Instance of a database you should leave your code as is. See [this answer](https://stackoverflow.com/a/11993118/5899345) for a precise difference between Static methods and Instance methods.

